name: Georgia
notes: Georgia uses ABC1234 format since May 2012. Features dual design system: peach tree graphic or plain peach background. Letter O excluded in current series. County stickers at top of plate. Multiple specialty plates with 2-letter prefixes. Does not use letter 'O' on standard plates. Always use zero '0'.
